The,TomTom,Camera,Media,Server,API,is,a,RESTful,platform,for,accessing,the,media,server,functionalities,of,the,TomTom,Bandit,Action,Cam,The,API,is,equipped,with,innovative,camera,features,such,as,remote,control,and,low,latency,viewfinder,functionality,that,support,the,performance,of,different,tasks,Its,features,can,be,used,to,tag,download,extract,sensor,data,and,preview,video,and,photo,content,Developers,must,have,and,turn,on,the,TomTom,Bandit,Wi,Fi,to,be,able,to,deploy,this,API,Its,requests,and,responses,are,transmitted,in,HTTP,and,JSON,formats,respectively